"""
        Test that the equality operator returns False when comparing two
        SignatureVerify response payloads with different validity indicators.
        """
a = signature_verify.SignatureVerifyResponsePayload(validity_indicator=
    enums.ValidityIndicator.VALID)
b = signature_verify.SignatureVerifyResponsePayload(validity_indicator=
    enums.ValidityIndicator.INVALID)
self.assertFalse(a == b)
self.assertFalse(b == a)
